                <div class='w-full md:max-w-md '>
                    <h3 class='mb-8 md:mb-0 text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold text-gray-700'>Why the API Middleware?</h3>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class='text-gray-500 max-w-md text-sm'>
                        The API Middleware is a next generation of gateway that embrace the bidirectional nature of APIs—securing, monitoring, logging, and managing your downstream traffic as well as upstream.
                    </p>
